			<description><![CDATA[<p>
Thrive Marketing Group is a small Nashville-based marketing company that offers performance marketing solutions for any industry. We specialize in lead generation, display, social &amp; email marketing, video production and web design.</p>
<p>
Thrive is seeking a Marketing Campaign Administrator to help facilitate our lead generation process.&nbsp; You will work with our fulfillment team to manage campaigns.&nbsp; The ideal candidate is a driven, success-oriented team player that thrives in a fast-paced environment.</p>
<p>
Your core responsibilities include setting up, maintaining, and delivering campaigns&mdash; simply put, moving high volumes of data through our complex system and delivering it to our clients. You will coordinate with a team to assist in email marketing initiatives including writing email creatives, developing and reviewing proofs for clients, managing follow up emails, and generating reports.</p>
<p>
We need a perfectionist who is able to work proficiently and keep the big picture in mind.&nbsp; We&rsquo;ll teach you the process and how to work with big data.</p>
<p>
<br />
<strong>Qualifications:</strong></p>
<p>
&bull; Mastery of Excel.<br />
&bull; Impeccable attention to detail.<br />
&bull; Efficient with computers.<br />
&bull; Excellent analytical and problem-solving skills.<br />
&bull; Strong verbal and written communication skills.<br />
&bull; Ability to learn new business processes or application nuances very quickly.<br />
&bull; Email marketing experience preferred.</p>
<p>
&nbsp;</p>
<p>
Pre-employment screening required.</p>
